<dl id="n40051b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40051b">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40051b"> 51(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> bitter lake </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: In the Chad basin of Middle Sudan, west of Mao, are a series of fertile valleys. Half of these are circular depressions having a bitter lake at the centre. The oblong wvalley (Sara) of Gala aloner is distinguished by a sweet water lake at its centre, free of reeds. </mm> </dd></dl>
